snippet.title: CouchFerret makes Games
snippet.description:
Are you interested in making games with Unity? 

Hi, I'm CouchFerret and follow me on my journey of indie game development. You will find in depth tutorials about developing games in Unity.
We will cover topics from programming to art and game design. Whether you are an expert or beginner, you will definitely find new tips and tricks about the whole game development process. These how to videos help you learn unity to develop 2d and 3d games on your own.

Stay tuned and consider subscribing!
